<?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/header.php"); ?><div class="root container responsivegrid">  <div class="" id="page">     <div class="container-wrapper">                             <div id="container-e3b79df8d7" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="container responsivegrid">  <div class="">     <div class="container-wrapper main-container">                             <div id="container-e79a3d1394" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="rich-text">            </div> <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component None None">     <div class="text"> <div class="row section"><h1>BLAST Poker</h1><div><h2>What is BLAST Sit &amp; Go?</h2><p>BLAST is a 3-handed, Super-turbo, Texas Hold’em Sit &amp; Go.</p><p>The prize pool of each BLAST Sit &amp; Go is determined by a draw that takes place at the beginning of each BLAST tournament and varies between two and 10,000 times the buy-in of the selected BLAST Sit &amp; Go game.</p><p>The starting chips, blind structure and prize pool distribution of each BLAST Sit &amp; Go is determined by the multiplier that was randomly assigned to that BLAST Sit &amp; Go game. The higher the multiplier, the deeper the structure.</p><h2>How to register for a BLAST Sit &amp; Go</h2><p>You’ll find the BLAST tab on the left side menu of 888poker.com’s main lobby.</p><p>Under this tab you’ll find all the available BLAST Sit &amp; Go buy-ins.</p><p>In order to register for a BLAST Sit &amp; Go, simply click on the buy-in you wish to play and select the amount of BLAST Sit &amp; Go tournaments you would like to register for.</p><p>Once 3 players have registered - the draw takes place and the game begins.</p><h2>The Draw</h2><p>The BLAST draw takes place as soon as the BLAST Sit &amp; Go starts and is what determines the prize pool.</p><p>The multiplier is randomly determined according to the probability tables below:</p><h2>Probability tables</h2><div class="Table" contentexport="tableCo